{
  "texts": [
    "Panel unit root tests are employed to test whether the underlying temperature change data has panels containing a unit root.",
    "However, our finding suggests that there is no evidence of unit root.",
    "The evidence suggests there is a negative impact from 2 to 4 years.",
    "The shock is a one standard deviation increase in risk.",
    "These can be convert to one unit shocks by dividing by the standard deviation of the original series."
  ]
}